Sample1
  socket connection establish
  client gets message from server
  the server serves one client at a time

Sample2
  socket connection establish
  server gets message from client
  the server serves one client at a time

Sample3: Simple Chat Server (Thread)
  the server serves multiple clients at the same time
  the server can handle clients' connection, receive message, and send message at the same time
  the clients can send and receive message at the same time
